{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be modern and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Financial Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c0392b;\n            --secondary-color: #e74c3c;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --light-gray: #333333;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light-gray);\n        }\n\n        section:last-of-type {\n            border-bottom: none;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--light-gray);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--light-gray);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            width: 80%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            background-color: var(--light-gray);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Financial Consulting</h1>\n            <p>Your Partner in Strategic Financial Growth</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">At Apex Financial Consulting, we provide expert financial advisory services to businesses of all sizes. Our seasoned professionals are dedicated to helping you navigate complex financial landscapes, optimize your operations, and achieve sustainable growth. We believe in a personalized approach, tailoring our strategies to meet your unique challenges and objectives.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Investment Strategy</h3>\n                    <p>Develop and implement robust investment plans to maximize returns and mitigate risks.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-dollar-sign\"></i>\n                    <h3>Financial Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Comprehensive financial planning services to ensure long-term stability and profitability.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-building\"></i>\n                    <h3>Corporate Finance</h3>\n                    <p>Expert guidance on mergers, acquisitions, capital raising, and other corporate financial needs.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                    <h3>Risk Management</h3>\n                    <p>Identify and manage financial risks to protect your assets and ensure business continuity.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"6\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Financial Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}